Description:
ONLY 400sqm BLOCK LEFT IN POINT COOK ! MUST SECURE !!! Titled Land in Upper Point Cook for your Dream Home!
Dont miss out on your opportunity to buy this excellent block of 400sqm (approx) land in the most popular Upper Point Cook. A block of land this with 12.5m frontage & 32m depth means you can build your dream home, and still have plenty of space for a beautiful outdoor entertaining area, and room for the kids to run around and play.
Upper Point Cook is the best positioned estate west of Melbourne, with everything you and your family need.
Nestled in the established suburb of Point Cook, this masterplanned community offers the perfect place for families to grow in space and comfort.
Eventually, around 2,000 families will call Upper Point Cook home, along with 14 hectares of open space, parks and playgrounds, walking trails, cycling paths and a future neighbourhood park.
One of the most impressive features of Upper Point Cook is the abundance of open space. There are stunning parks and wetlands throughout, contributing to 14 hectares of open space within the community. And you can make the most of all this outdoor space with amenities such as playgrounds, cycling tracks and walking paths.
For families, there are also two proposed child care centres within the estate.
Youll also be just a five minute drive from the Point Cook town centre, close to primary and secondary schools and have a direct connection to the Princes Freeway via Sneydes Road
Don't miss this opportunity call INDER on 0413 200 235 !
